quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  8,70,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, maakan dahaa…ďe wonu…ďe e juu…óe mon …ďen : \"Si Alla no anndi mo∆ī∆īere ka …ďer…óe mon, O okkay on ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko ja…ďano…óon kon, O haforana on. Alla ko haforoowo hinnotoo…óo"
  8,71,"Si …ďe faandike janfagol ma, gom…óii …ďe janfinoke Alla ko adii; O newinan (maa) e mab…ďe. Alla ko Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  8,72,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe, …ďe feri …ďe tii…ónorii jawle ma…ď…ďe e wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe fii laawol Alla, e …ďen weernu …ďe walli (…ďe); …ďen …óon yoga ma…ď…ďe ko walloo…ďe yoga. ∆Āen non gom…óim…ďe kono …ďe feraali, alanaa on wallugol …ďe hay e huunde haa …ďe fera. Si …ďe wallinorii on ka diina, no fawii on wallitagol (…ďe), si wanaa hara ko e yim…ďe …ďe ahadi woni hakkunde mon e ma…ď…ďe. Alla ko reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  8,73,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe, yoga ma…ď…ďe ko walloo…ďe yoga. Si on w…óaali …óum [ko Mi …óa…ď…ďiri on wallugol gom…óim…ďe …ďen ayra e heefer…ďe …ďen], wonay fitina ka leydi e bone maw…óo"
  8,74,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe, …ďe feri …ďe tii…ónii e laawol Alla ngol, e …ďen weernu …ďe walli (…ďe); ko …ďen woni gom…óim…ďe goonga …ďen: no woodani …ďe haforanal e arsike teddu…óo"
  8,75,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe …ďaawo (…óum), …ďe feri …ďe tii…ónodii e mon, …ďen …óon ko jeyaa…ďe e mon. Joomiraa…ďe en…óammaaji …ďen (ko) yoga ma…ď…ďe …ďuri hanndude e yoga ka Deftere Alla. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
